<p class="kicker">Selected work / album</p>
<h1 class="h1">The Insomnia Club</h1>
<p class="lede"><em>The Insomnia Club</em> is an earlier released album that shows Charlotte’s first public step as a recording artist. It sits in the portfolio as background to her current major project, <a href="/work/family-business/"><em>Family Business</em></a>, which is the latest and more developed body of work for this submission.</p>

